{"tid":922293,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"同班廢老去旅行慘過番工","createTime":"2018-11-30T09:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T09:55:30.000Z","uid":173334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1096fde217ce1038825ebe00c54f0acc15acefbd","tid":922293,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:11:26.000Z","msg":"1. 行程唔plan又冇比意見。去到嫌3嫌4， 呢樣果樣！<br />\n2. 行得快又話唔等佢，大佬，行快幾步探路，一陣行錯又話9我<br />\n3. 成程依依哦哦，又長氣又煩，唔順佢意就complain 西口西面 , 好似全世界欠佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 持老賣老，乜都好似老馮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 樣樣斤斤計較，一齊用錢 之後又話你用多話佢 呢樣果樣 <br />\n6. 乜都嫌貴 去得旅行就洗錢嫁啦 屌<br />\n7. 食野麻q煩 樣樣都話唔岩食 <br />\n8. 晨早起身 話等你出門等到餓。有手有腳 唔識自己搵野食？<br />\n9. 只顧自己感受 為旅行係為氹班廢老開心 就可以為所欲為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二次？ 不了 屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c941efcdcbdd1495b15223961d65ab501cb3f49","tid":922293,"uid":6833,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"同老人家去旅行一定要跟團"},{"pid":"c68ee453dab4692a00c6c3a43a28b53f2e9c2095","tid":922293,"uid":173334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8c941efcdcbdd1495b15223961d65ab501cb3f49","tid":922293,"uid":6833,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"同老人家去旅行一定要跟團"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"比錢佢地自己同朋友跟團 咪再搞我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20571d6c0eeefb920034ebcf7cbcab1d43d778cc","tid":922293,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68ee453dab4692a0